{
  "rationale": "To ensure safe and efficient coverage, we explicitly track obstacle encounters and recent rotations, introducing a helper state 'recent_rot' to prevent oscillations and promote systematic exploration. All states handle uncontrollable events, and forward/random_walk is only allowed when clear. Rotations are used to resolve obstacles, and full_rotate is employed if stuck.",
